&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovuwbz84zn3z90z5az81zz86zz67zz122z3z82zxnpiz72zz77zz69zz77zekw00jz83z6&quot;&gt;Self-starter mindset with the ability to operate effectively in a fast-paced, evolving environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
