&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxwz73zz68ziz122zhv2z67zqodz78zz122zz122ztz88zdkz69zz68zz77zqg5vz66zsc18&quot;&gt;Represent Dropbox at key industry events and customer engagements for selected customer accounts, delivering presentations and supporting our sales teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
