&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8oz81zy7z86zz74zcbz65zz86z2z89zz85zels1l7wz70zoz70zz76z36z73zz69zz71z&quot;&gt;Strong strategic mindset &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxwz73zz68ziz122zhv2z67zqodz78zz122zz122ztz88zdkz69zz68zz77zqg5vz66zsc18&quot;&gt;with the ability to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8oz81zy7z86zz74zcbz65zz86z2z89zz85zels1l7wz70zoz70zz76z36z73zz69zz71z&quot;&gt; Dropbox’s goals with emerging opportunities in t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxwz73zz68ziz122zhv2z67zqodz78zz122zz122ztz88zdkz69zz68zz77zqg5vz66zsc18&quot;&gt;his industry&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8oz81zy7z86zz74zcbz65zz86z2z89zz85zels1l7wz70zoz70zz76z36z73zz69zz71z&quot;&gt;Excellent project management and cross-functional leadership skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8oz81zy7z86zz74zcbz65zz86z2z89zz85zels1l7wz70zoz70zz76z36z73zz69zz71z&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s degree required; relevant postgraduate qualification preferre&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxwz73zz68ziz122zhv2z67zqodz78zz122zz122ztz88zdkz69zz68zz77zqg5vz66zsc18&quot;&gt;d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
